    • disabled

      LinkBuilder disabled()
      Disable the link. This is currently only used for style sheet links, and may be used to deactivate style sheets.

    • href

      LinkBuilder href(String href)
      The URI of the linked resource. The @IsTrustedResourceUri is added conservatively in case href points to a stylesheet.
